text: Patrick Murphy may mean * Patrick Murphy (biker), Canadian Olympic Biker. * Patrick Murphy (giant), Irish Giant. * Patrick Murphy (Irish Politician), Irish Politician from Cork. * Patrick Murphy (coach), Softball coach. * Patrick Murphy (pilot) Irish pilot. * Patrick Murphy (swimmer), Olympic swimmer from Australia. * G.
